Trustees and Staff
Meet the people working to support our grantees and help them advance change.








                All the philosophy about our Mott Foundation can be boiled down to just one word — people.                  C.S. Harding Mott








Leadership Two generations — and 60 years of experience — guide our foundation into the future. 




Mott Foundation Chairman and CEO William S. White (right) congratulates Ridgway White on being appointed Foundation president.











