Annual Reports





Media Center





























February 17, 2017
                       | Flint Area                  

2015 Annual Report | Flint: reflections on crisis, community and commitment in Mott’s hometown


The Mott Foundation’s latest annual report explores the value of endowed philanthropy and the importance of partnerships in helping communities deal with ordinary challenges and extraordinary crises. 














December 23, 2015


2014 Annual Report | Inspiring change: portraits of partnership


The Mott Foundation 2014 annual report explores four inspiring “portraits” of people who have engaged with their communities to create positive change. 














January 20, 2015
                       | Environment                  

2013 Annual Report | Toward sustainability: helping communities engage with and protect the environment


The Mott Foundation’s 2013 annual report features first-hand perspectives of those working on the ground to protect the world’s precious natural resources. 














December 20, 2013
                       | Civil Society                  

2012 Annual Report | Community foundations: Rooted locally. Growing globally.


The Mott Foundation’s 2012 Annual Report examines the phenomenal growth of the community foundation field, as well as Mott’s long-standing commitment to it. 














December 1, 2012
                       | Education                  

2011 Annual Report | Picturing success: the transformative power of afterschool


The Mott Foundation’s 2011 Annual Report takes an in-depth look at our commitment to increasing the quality and availability of afterschool programming. 














