Charles Stewart Mott Foundation - Wikipedia




















 






Charles Stewart Mott Foundation

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Charles Stewart Mott Foundation

Formation
1926


Type
Charitable Foundation


Headquarters
Flint, M, United States



Chairman and CEO

William S. White



Revenue (2015)

$228,269,796[1]


Expenses (2015)
$145,634,783[1]


